<item>
            <title>[LU-1610] LND threads tunable should be for overall threads number, not threads number for each CPT pool</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1610</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Current LND threads tunable (ksocklnd, ko2iblnd) are threads number for each partition, which is inconvenient because number of CPTs could be various, also we need to change it to be overall threads number before releasing of 2.3.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
